data.title: Film Forum · TEST TUBE BABIES
data.meta_description:
TEST TUBE BABIES
Saturday, March 9 10:10

New Restoration

(1948, W. Merle Connell) A pair of newlyweds struggles with infertility, until they get a biology lesson from delightfully deadpan Timothy Farrell. Any remaining questions will be answered by a “square-up” reel featuring color footage of surgical childbirth. DCP. Approx. 75 min.
